{"tid":1842604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"見到d垃圾親戚SD 偏方來，話可以阻隔肺炎。","createTime":"2020-01-25T19:19:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T20:49:35.000Z","uid":275677,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"30f633687c42df49a75f988d552a07b785132b7a","tid":1842604,"uid":275677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T19:19:38.000Z","msg":"敬请快速转发此信息:<br />\n正骨医院郭氏孙女郭艳娟（过去的同事，現三门峡正骨分院院长）所发分享给大家：<br />\n给大家透漏个家传秘密，每天出门前用棉签蘸点小磨香油，滴进两个鼻孔内，轻捏几下即可，这样就可以阻断一切流感和温疫传染，这是我家不传之秘决，今告知大家，望大家过一个快乐，祥和的春节。<br />\n   民国27年河南瘟疫，死人无数，我爷爷就是每天这样给别人看病，救人无数，当时也没口罩之说，就是这种方法阻断传染，十分有效，故作秘传。（方子土了些，土方管用）<br />\n<br />\n幾時可以用童子尿，狗屎都醫到病<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64789cbf82e8195829c4ab38afa6e560a11197a0","tid":1842604,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T19:22:29.000Z","msg":":0)........"},{"pid":"82b864c608505d6e0d249c2da371901971204362","tid":1842604,"uid":301384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T19:24:08.000Z","msg":"借個位，幫推<br />\n[唔想死，唔想害死人嘅入黎]你地系唔系唔記得沙士點爆，屌你正系帶口罩有撚用咩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1842516\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1842516</a>"},{"pid":"b1b52f00f9e4a414671ea4b75ad2db3016c27026","tid":1842604,"uid":15605,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T19:29:21.000Z","msg":"夜明砂可以醫肺炎，叫佢快啲去買"},{"pid":"5789b0a6a06c23f837d3ace906105af4ffcf0d1a","tid":1842604,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T19:36:13.000Z","msg":"係生食蝙蝠吸收抗體。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b527b9022f5c423dec3f563c24013638cfcb045c","tid":1842604,"uid":202867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T19:37:33.000Z",